How to fix shutdown  frezzing  problem in your ubantu system 

How to fix it :-

step1:- open terminal (CTRL+ALT+T)
step2:- type sudo gedit /etc/default/grub/
step3:-  just change GRUB_CMDLINE_LINUX_DEFAULT="quiet splash" into GRUB_CMDLINE_LINUX_DEFAULT="quiet splash acpi=force"
step4:- Save It 
step5:- sudo update-grub
step6:- Boot system / Restart System
